description:
Squid collection points + ability to move squid vertically = automatic & convenient squid farm.

Moving squid vertically is simple really. I'm sure many people tried this method before with no success. However, a recent patch seems to have changed squid behavior so that they can move up half slabs, stairs, and fences.

This makes it possible to automatically gather and harvest squid any where you may choose.
